dialogue: Let's go around the table and introduce ourselves.
I'm always afraid I'll forget my name when the pressure is on me.
...And I've been in the integrated design district for four years.
People are saying where they work.
I can't remember the name of my district.
Aaagh! Now they're adding witty comments.
My only chance is to pretend I only speak Norwegian.
Norna borna corna dorna fiord cajorda ha ha ha!
The amazing thing is that I get paid the same no matter what I do.
